{"about_the_game":"It's just hoops... Or is it?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2547940/extras/Artboard_5.png?t=1706056181\" /><br><br>Relax and shoot some hoops in a variety of scenic locations. Choose from basic courts, or courts with challenging trick shots &amp; long shots! <br><br>Immerse yourself in the world of first-person basketball, where players can test their shooting abilities on a range of courts. <br><br>Drawing inspiration from iconic shooter titles that included hidden (and often overlooked) basketball mini-games and physics-based novelty features, Hoops World allows you to discover the joy of sinking hoops and trick-shots in unique locations such as indoor courts, stadiums, beaches, and more!<br><br>Transforming a classic, quirky gaming element into a full-fledged FPS basketball experience, Hoops World is a great way to relax in your own world!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2547940/extras/Artboard_6.png?t=1706056181\" /><br><br>Along with various basketball courts and locations, Hoops World includes physics-based fun!<br><br>Drive vehicles around various racetracks, drifting and sliding around a variety of scenic locations in between sinking hoops and exploring! <br><br>Find many different physics-based objects to play around with. <strong>Hoops World</strong> is <strong>your world</strong> - play any way you like!","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2547940/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1706056181","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2547940/page.bg.jpg?t=1706056181","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2547940/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1706056181","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2547940/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1706056181","c